videos.headline: Jones II opens the scoring for USC with quick rushing TD
videos.description: Ronald Jones II  rushes in for a 16-yard score early in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Jamauri Bogan run for 4 yds for a TD (Josh Grant KICK)
videos.description: J. Bogan run for 4 yds for a TD, (J. Grant KICK)

videos.headline: Wassink's TD gets WMU the lead over USC
videos.description: WMU QB Jon Wassink takes a hit from three USC defenders while diving in for the touchdown WMU lead 14-7.

videos.headline: Jones II dives for the short TD
videos.description: Ronald Jones II ties the game with a one-yard rushing touchdown 14-14.

videos.headline: Darnold pass tipped and picked off by WMU to end the half
videos.description: Darius Phillips intercepts Sam Darnold and returns it 20 yards at the end of the half.

videos.headline: Helton: 'USC Offense a little sloppy'
videos.description: USC Head Coach Clay Helton talks about Trojans poor performance in the first half.

videos.headline: WMU converts on flea flicker to take the lead
videos.description: Jon Wassink throws to Keishawn Watson, who throws back to Wassink for a 27-yard touchdown to take the lead.

videos.headline: Darnold picked off again
videos.description: After review, Sam Beal keeps his feet inbounds on interception for WMU.

videos.headline: Burnett diving catch for USC
videos.description: Deontay Burnett gets low on a 27-yard pass over the middle from Sam Darnold.

videos.headline: Darnold rushing TD ties the game
videos.description: Sam Darnold takes it in from 11 yards out for the rushing touchdown to tie the game at 21-21.

videos.headline: Carr gives USC the lead with TD
videos.description: Stephen Carr puts USC ahead with a one-yard rushing touchdown USC 28-21.

videos.headline: Phillips returns kickoff all the way for the TD
videos.description: WMU return specialist Darius Phillips returns the kickoff 100 yards for the TD to tie the game with USC.

videos.headline: Darnold finds Burnett open for 46 yards
videos.description: Sam Darnold throws to an open Deontay Burnett to get inside WMU territory.

videos.headline: Jones II breaks tackles for a big score, 3rd TD today
videos.description: Ronald Jones II beats multiple defenders to give USC the lead on his third TD of the day.

videos.headline: Bellamy with a huge run into USC territory
videos.description: After review, it's ruled LeVante Bellamy keeps the ball after running for 48 yards.

videos.headline: Carr extends USC lead with big run
videos.description: Stephen Carr goes 52-yards to score as USC lead builds to 42-31.

videos.headline: USC puts the game out of reach with pick-6
videos.description: Marvell Tell III picks off Jon Wassink for a 37-yard return for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Blind USC long snapper enters game
videos.description: Jake Olson makes the snap on USC's final extra point. Olson lost his vision at the age of 12 due to cancer.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blind USC long snapper enters game) 2017/09/03

videos.headline: USC holds off Western Michigan
videos.description: Ronald Jones II rushes for 159 yards and three scores to lead No. 4 USC past Western Michigan in a 49-31 win.

videos.headline: USC's Olson embraced by family after game
videos.description: Long snapper Jake Olson, who has been blind since age 12, snapped for the first time today against Western Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc. (USC's Olson embraced by family after game) 2017/9/2 shortstop OnScene

videos.headline: Olson's emotional journey to the field
videos.description: Blind long-snapper Jake Olson, a member of the USC football family since the age of 12, takes the field for a "special" moment.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Olson's emotional journey to the field) 2017/9/3 ESHEET ENHL
